  <brief_title>Study of VSN16R for the Treatment of Spasticity in Multiple Sclerosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II Proof of Concept (PoC), Double-Blind, Randomised, Placebo-controlled Study to Evaluate the Efficacy, Safety, and Pharmacokinetics of VSN16R for the Treatment of Spasticity in Subjects With Multiple Sclerosis</official_title>
