  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Phase II a Proof of concept study in Multiple Sclerosis (MS) patients with spasticity.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Single dose escalation followed by multiple fixed dose administrations to assess short term
      safety and to determine whether spasticity improves.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
